Entries.default: "Ten galleons and five days of cannonfire could not have caused this much destruction."
"Oh, dear. This is even worse than Port Maje."
"Looks like this went about as well as you'd expect."
"The Sorcerer plundered a parcel of powder headed here once. This sad sight almost be making me feel guilty."
"It was hubris to settle in a reef full of snakes. Rauatai can take a lesson from this."
"This here's a lesson learned, I'm betting. But at what cost?"
